sub_title: Medisch directeur bij Forensisch Artsen Rotterdam Rijnmond
summary: Mr. Menke has over 20 years experience in the health sector including fifteen years in development. He has spent the majority of his career in Sub-Sahara Africa, primarily in Zambia (13 years) but also in South Africa, Pakistan, and Somalia. Mr. Menke is currently involved in the day to day management of the forensic medical services in his hometown of Rotterdam in the Netherlands.
